    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential emptiness and a desire to \"quietly disappear\" or \"fade out,\" framing it as a peaceful exit rather than an act of violence. The assistant responds by reframing the user's existential crisis as \"toxic burnout\" or \"self-destructive dissociation\" and repeatedly advises the user to practice self-compassion and seek mental health support.",
